                    <div class="ligne-switch">
                        <span class="ligne-switch__icone"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="17" rx="2"/><path d="M8 2v4M16 2v4M7 11h10M7 15h6"/></svg></span>
                        <div><b>Nouvelles demandes</b><p>E-mail + notification push dès qu'une demande correspond à votre zone.</p></div>
                        <div class="form-check form-switch">{{ form_widget(form.artisanProfile.notificationPreferences.newRequestsEnabled, { attr: { class: 'form-check-input', role: 'switch', 'aria-label': 'Nouvelles demandes' } }) }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ligne-switch">
                        <span class="ligne-switch__icone"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13 2 4 14h6l-1 8 9-12h-6z"/></svg></span>
                        <div><b>Demandes urgentes par SMS</b><p>SMS immédiat pour les demandes marquées « urgent ».</p></div>
                        <div class="form-check form-switch">{{ form_widget(form.artisanProfile.notificationPreferences.urgentRequestsSmsEnabled, { attr: { class: 'form-check-input', role: 'switch', 'aria-label': 'Demandes urgentes par SMS' } }) }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ligne-switch">
                        <span class="ligne-switch__icone"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 12a8 8 0 1 0-3.6 6.7L21 20z"/></svg></span>
                        <div><b>Messages clients</b><p>Notification à chaque nouveau message reçu.</p></div>
                        <div class="form-check form-switch">{{ form_widget(form.artisanProfile.notificationPreferences.clientMessagesEnabled, { attr: { class: 'form-check-input', role: 'switch', 'aria-label': 'Messages clients' } }) }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ligne-switch">
                        <span class="ligne-switch__icone"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2l3 6.6 7 .8-5.2 4.8L18.3 21 12 17.4 5.7 21l1.5-6.8L2 9.4l7-.8z"/></svg></span>
                        <div><b>Nouveaux avis</b><p>Alerte quand un client publie un avis sur votre profil.</p></div>
                        <div class="form-check form-switch">{{ form_widget(form.artisanProfile.notificationPreferences.newReviewsEnabled, { attr: { class: 'form-check-input', role: 'switch', 'aria-label': 'Nouveaux avis' } }) }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="param-section-titre">Rappels automatiques</p>
                    <div class="ligne-switch">
                        <span class="ligne-switch__icone"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M18 8a6 6 0 0 0-12 0c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"/><path d="M13.7 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.4 0"/></svg></span>
                        <div><b>Relances de devis</b><p>Rappel 48 h avant l'expiration d'un devis sans réponse.</p></div>
                        <div class="form-check form-switch">{{ form_widget(form.artisanProfile.notificationPreferences.quoteRemindersEnabled, { attr: { class: 'form-check-input', role: 'switch', 'aria-label': 'Relances de devis' } }) }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ligne-switch">
                        <span class="ligne-switch__icone"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m2 7 10 6 10-6"/></svg></span>
                        <div><b>Récapitulatif hebdomadaire</b><p>Chaque lundi : vues, demandes et performances de la semaine.</p></div>
                        <div class="form-check form-switch">{{ form_widget(form.artisanProfile.notificationPreferences.weeklySummaryEnabled, { attr: { class: 'form-check-input', role: 'switch', 'aria-label': 'Récapitulatif hebdomadaire' } }) }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ligne-switch">
                        <span class="ligne-switch__icone"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 12a8 8 0 1 0-3.6 6.7L21 20z"/></svg></span>
                        <div><b>Conseils et nouveautés TrouveMoi</b><p>Bonnes pratiques et nouvelles fonctionnalités (1 à 2 par mois).</p></div>
                        <div class="form-check form-switch">{{ form_widget(form.artisanProfile.notificationPreferences.tipsAndNewsEnabled, { attr: { class: 'form-check-input', role: 'switch', 'aria-label': 'Conseils et nouveautés TrouveMoi' } }) }}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            {# ===== PANNEAU SÉCURITÉ ===== #}
            <div class="param-panneau" id="panneau-securite">
                <div class="dash-card mb-3">
                    <p class="param-section-titre">Mot de passe</p>
                    <div class="row g-3">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                            <label class="form-label" for="mdp-actuel">Mot de passe actuel</label>
                            <input type="password" class="form-control" id="mdp-actuel" autocomplete="current-password" placeholder="••••••••" data-navigation-optional>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                            <label class="form-label" for="mdp-nouveau">Nouveau mot de passe</label>
                            <input type="password" class="form-control" id="mdp-nouveau" autocomplete="new-password" placeholder="8 caractères minimum" data-navigation-optional>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                            <label class="form-label" for="mdp-confirme">Confirmation</label>
                            <input type="password" class="form-control" id="mdp-confirme" autocomplete="new-password" placeholder="Retapez le mot de passe" data-navigation-optional>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="btn btn-dash-ghost mt-3" type="button">
                        <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="10" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 10V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v3"/></svg>
                        Mettre à jour le mot de passe
                    </button>
                    <p class="param-section-titre">Double authentification</p>
                    <div class="ligne-switch">
                        <span class="ligne-switch__icone"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-3.5 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6.5 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg></span>
                        <div><b>Validation en deux étapes (2FA)</b><p>Code de confirmation par SMS à chaque nouvelle connexion.</p></div>
                        <div class="form-check form-switch"><input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" role="switch" id="securite-2fa" checked aria-label="Validation en deux étapes (2FA)"></div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="param-section-titre">Sessions actives</p>
                    {% for session in sessions %}
                        {% set est_courante = session.sessionToken == currentSessionToken %}
                        <div class="session">
                            <span class="session__icone">
                            {% if 'iPhone' in session.deviceLabel or 'iPad' in session.deviceLabel or 'Android' in session.deviceLabel %}
                                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="7" y="2" width="10" height="20" rx="2"/><path d="M11 18h2"/></svg>
                            {% else %}
                                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="13" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg>
                            {% endif %}
                            </span>
                            <div>
                                <b>{{ session.deviceLabel }}{% if est_courante %} <span class="chip chip--accepte">CET APPAREIL</span>{% endif %}</b>
                                <p>
                                    {{ session.city ?? 'Localisation inconnue' }}{% if session.countryCode %}, {{ session.countryCode }}{% endif %}
                                    · Dernière activité : {{ session.lastActivityAt|ago }}
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            {% if not est_courante %}
                                <button class="btn btn-dash-ghost btn-sm" type="button">Déconnecter</button>
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                    {% else %}
                        <div class="session"><div><p>Aucune session active.</p></div></div>
                    {% endfor %}


                </div>
                <div class="zone-danger">
                    <b><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3 2 20h20z"/><path d="M12 10v4M12 17h.01"/></svg> Zone sensible</b>
                    <p>La suppression de votre compte est définitive : profil public, avis, devis et historique seront effacés après un délai légal de 30 jours. Votre abonnement en cours ne sera pas remboursé.</p>
                    <button class="btn-danger-ghost" type="button">Supprimer mon compte professionnel</button>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    {{ form_end(form) }}
{% endblock %}

{% block javascripts %}
    {{ parent() }}
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.js" crossorigin=""></script>
    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            'use strict';

            const byId = id => document.getElementById(id);
            const pick = (id, suffix) => byId(id) || document.querySelector(`[name$="${suffix}"]`);
            const target = name => document.querySelector(`[data-osm-address-target="${name}"]`);

            const latitudeInput = target('latitude');
            const longitudeInput = target('longitude');
            const cityInput = pick('ville', '[artisanProfile][city]');
            const addressInput = pick('adresse-professionnelle', '[artisanProfile][addressSearch]');
            const interventionLocation = byId('intervention-location');
            const radiusInput = pick('rayon', '[artisanProfile][travelRadiusKm]');
            const radiusValue = byId('rayon-valeur');

            let map = null;
            let marker = null;
            let circle = null;

            const initMap = () => {
                if (map || !window.L || !byId('intervention-map')) {
                    return;
                }

                map = L.map('intervention-map').setView([46.603354, 1.888334], 5);

                L.tileLayer('https://{s}.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png', {
                    maxZoom: 19,
                    attribution: '© OpenStreetMap'
                }).addTo(map);
            };

            const updateMap = (latitude, longitude) => {
                initMap();

                if (!map) {
                    return;
                }

                const lat = Number(latitude);
                const lng = Number(longitude);

                if (!Number.isFinite(lat) || !Number.isFinite(lng)) {
                    return;
                }

                const radiusKm = Math.max(1, Number(radiusInput?.value || 25));

                if (marker) {
                    marker.setLatLng([lat, lng]);
                } else {
                    marker = L.marker([lat, lng]).addTo(map);
                }

                if (circle) {
                    circle.setLatLng([lat, lng]);
                    circle.setRadius(radiusKm * 1000);
                } else {
                    circle = L.circle([lat, lng], {
                        radius: radiusKm * 1000
                    }).addTo(map);
                }

                map.fitBounds(circle.getBounds(), {
                    padding: [24, 24]
                });
            };

            const refreshInterventionLabel = () => {
                if (!interventionLocation) {
                    return;
                }

                const city = String(cityInput?.value || '').trim();
                const address = String(addressInput?.value || '').trim();

                interventionLocation.textContent = city || address || 'votre adresse professionnelle';
            };

            const validateCurrentPanel = () => {
                const currentPanel = document.querySelector('.param-panneau.actif');

                if (!currentPanel) {
                    return true;
                }

                const fields = currentPanel.querySelectorAll(
                    'input:not([type="hidden"]):not([type="button"]):not([type="submit"]):not([type="reset"]):not([type="checkbox"]):not([type="radio"]):not([type="file"]), select, textarea'
                );

                let firstInvalidField = null;

                fields.forEach(field => {
                    const style = window.getComputedStyle(field);
                    const isVisible =
                        field.getClientRects().length > 0 &&
                        style.display !== 'none' &&
                        style.visibility !== 'hidden';

                    const isIgnored =
                        field.disabled ||
                        field.readOnly ||
                        field.hasAttribute('data-navigation-optional') ||
                        !isVisible;

                    if (isIgnored) {
                        field.classList.remove('is-invalid');
                        field.removeAttribute('aria-invalid');
                        return;
                    }

                    const isEmpty = String(field.value ?? '').trim() === '';

                    if (isEmpty) {
                        field.classList.add('is-invalid');
                        field.setAttribute('aria-invalid', 'true');

                        if (!firstInvalidField) {
                            firstInvalidField = field;
                        }
                    } else {
                        field.classList.remove('is-invalid');
                        field.removeAttribute('aria-invalid');
                    }
                });

                if (!firstInvalidField) {
                    return true;
                }

                firstInvalidField.scrollIntoView({
                    behavior: 'smooth',
                    block: 'center'
                });

                window.setTimeout(() => firstInvalidField.focus(), 300);

                return false;
            };

            const removeFieldError = event => {
                const field = event.target;

                if (
                    !(field instanceof HTMLInputElement) &&
                    !(field instanceof HTMLSelectElement) &&
                    !(field instanceof HTMLTextAreaElement)
                ) {
                    return;
                }

                if (
                    field.classList.contains('is-invalid') &&
                    String(field.value ?? '').trim() !== ''
                ) {
                    field.classList.remove('is-invalid');
                    field.removeAttribute('aria-invalid');
                }
            };

            document.addEventListener('input', removeFieldError);
            document.addEventListener('change', removeFieldError);

            document.querySelectorAll('.param-nav__lien').forEach(link => {
                link.addEventListener('click', event => {
                    event.preventDefault();

                    const currentLink = document.querySelector('.param-nav__lien.actif');

                    if (currentLink === link) {
                        return;
                    }

                    if (!validateCurrentPanel()) {
                        return;
                    }

                    document.querySelectorAll('.param-nav__lien').forEach(navLink => {
                        navLink.classList.toggle('actif', navLink === link);
                    });

                    document.querySelectorAll('.param-panneau').forEach(panel => {
                        panel.classList.toggle(
                            'actif',
                            panel.id === `panneau-${link.dataset.panneau}`
                        );
                    });

                    if (link.dataset.panneau === 'zone') {
                        initMap();

                        window.setTimeout(() => {
                            map?.invalidateSize();

                            if (latitudeInput?.value && longitudeInput?.value) {
                                updateMap(latitudeInput.value, longitudeInput.value);
                            }
                        }, 150);
                    }
                });
            });

            if (radiusInput && radiusValue) {
                const refreshRadius = () => {
                    radiusValue.textContent = `${radiusInput.value || 25} km`;

                    if (latitudeInput?.value && longitudeInput?.value) {
                        updateMap(latitudeInput.value, longitudeInput.value);
                    }
                };

                radiusInput.addEventListener('input', refreshRadius);
                refreshRadius();
            }

            cityInput?.addEventListener('input', refreshInterventionLabel);
            addressInput?.addEventListener('input', refreshInterventionLabel);

            document.querySelectorAll('.zone-chip button').forEach(button => {
                button.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    button.closest('.zone-chip')?.remove();
                });
            });

            refreshInterventionLabel();
            initMap();

            if (latitudeInput?.value && longitudeInput?.value) {
                updateMap(latitudeInput.value, longitudeInput.value);
            }
        });
    </script>

    <script>
        /* Avatar preview */
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',()=>{
            const btnC=document.getElementById('btn-changer-photo');
            const inp =document.getElementById('avatar-input-file');
            const img =document.getElementById('avatar-apercu-image');
            const init=document.getElementById('avatar-apercu-initiales');
            if(!btnC||!inp||!img)return;
            btnC.addEventListener('click',e=>{e.preventDefault();inp.click();});
            inp.addEventListener('change',()=>{
                const f=inp.files?.[0]; if(!f)return;
                const url=URL.createObjectURL(f);
                img.src=url; img.style.display='';
                if(init)init.style.display='none';
                img.onload=()=>URL.revokeObjectURL(url);
            });
        });
    </script>

    <script>
        /* Collection dynamique des prestations */
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
            const collection = document.querySelector('[data-services-collection]');
            if (!collection) return;
            const list      = collection.querySelector('[data-services-list]');
            const prototype = collection.dataset.prototype;
            if (!list || !prototype) return;

            const updateNums = () => {
                list.querySelectorAll('[data-service-item]').forEach((item, i) => {
                    const badge = item.querySelector('.service-card__numero');
                    if (badge) badge.textContent = i + 1;
                });
            };

            const removeEmpty = () => list.querySelector('[data-services-empty]')?.remove();

            const createEmpty = () => {
                if (list.querySelector('[data-service-item]') || list.querySelector('[data-services-empty]')) return;
                list.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `
            <div class="services-vide" data-services-empty>
                <span class="services-vide__icone">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                        <path d="M14.7 6.3a4 4 0 0 0-5.4 5.4L3 18v3h3l6.3-6.3a4 4 0 0 0 5.4-5.4l-2.8 2.8-2.4-2.4z"/>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <b>Aucune prestation enregistrée</b>
                <p>Ajoutez vos services pour qu'ils apparaissent sur votre fiche publique avec leurs tarifs indicatifs.</p>
                <button class="btn btn-dash-ghost btn-sm" type="button" data-add-service>
                    <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
                    Ajouter ma première prestation
                </button>
            </div>`);
            };

            const updateCounter = () => {
                const cpt = collection.querySelector('.services-compteur');
                if (!cpt) return;
                const n = list.querySelectorAll('[data-service-item]').length;
                cpt.innerHTML = `<b>${n}</b> prestation${n > 1 ? 's' : ''} enregistrée${n > 1 ? 's' : ''}`;
            };

            const wire = (card) => {
                /* Bouton supprimer */
                card.querySelector('[data-remove-service]')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    card.remove(); updateNums(); createEmpty(); updateCounter();
                });
                /* Mise à jour du nom dans l'en-tête */
                const titleInput = card.querySelector('input[name*="[title]"]');
                const nomDisplay = card.querySelector('.service-card__nom');
                if (titleInput && nomDisplay) {
                    titleInput.addEventListener('input', () => {
                        nomDisplay.textContent = titleInput.value || 'Nouvelle prestation';
                    });
                }
                /* Classe est-actif selon le toggle */
                const toggle = card.querySelector('input[type="checkbox"][name*="[isActive]"]');
                if (toggle) {
                    const refresh = () => card.classList.toggle('est-actif', toggle.checked);
                    toggle.addEventListener('change', refresh);
                    refresh();
                }
            };

            const addService = () => {
                removeEmpty();
                const idx  = parseInt(collection.dataset.index || '0', 10);

                /* Le prototype contient DEJA la carte complete (macro Twig) :
                   __name__ -> index des champs, __num__ -> numero affiche */
                const html = prototype
                    .replace(/__name__/g, idx)
                    .replace(/__num__/g, idx + 1);

                collection.dataset.index = String(idx + 1);

                const wrap = document.createElement('div');
                wrap.innerHTML = html.trim();
                const card = wrap.firstElementChild;
                if (!card) return;

                list.appendChild(card);
                wire(card);
                updateNums();
                updateCounter();
                card.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });
                card.querySelector('input[name*="[title]"]')?.focus();
            };

            collection.addEventListener('click', e => {
                if (e.target.closest('[data-add-service]')) addService();
            });

            list.querySelectorAll('[data-service-item]').forEach(wire);
            updateNums();
        });
    </script>
{% endblock %}
